 during major events throughout France's history, from the construction of the Notre-Dame cathedral in 1163 to the Revolution of 1789 to the lastParis Olympics in 1924.\", \"from\": 1427, \"to\": 1641, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1453, \"end\": 1461, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phrygian_cap\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.165110955762344e-14, \"text\": \"Phrygian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phrygian_cap\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phrygian_cap\"}, {\"begin\": 1508, \"end\": 1514, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999427828580428, \"rank\": 4.330927933320356e-05, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The caps can also be seen in busts of French icon Marianne across the country, as well as on coins and stamps.\", \"from\": 1642, \"to\": 1752, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1683, \"end\": 1689, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.6867629071907052, \"rank\": 0.29164363944284527, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1690, \"end\": 1694, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Symbol\", \"score\": 0.9507214407183353, \"rank\": 0.05162527102009542, \"text\": \"icon\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Symbol\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Symbol\"}, {\"begin\": 1695, \"end\": 1703, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marianne\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4249436544690006e-37, \"text\": \"Marianne\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marianne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marianne\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We chose an ideal rather than an animal,\\\" said Tony Estanguet, 2024 Paris Olympics president